juju-installer (0.1.6) noble; urgency=medium

  * Fix: add pre-snap-install disk-space check (5 GiB on /var) to both LXD
    and K8s service scripts. Aborts cleanly with an actionable message
    before juju/k8s bootstrap fails opaquely on tight-disk hosts.
  * Fix: anchor the K8s cluster-readiness fallback regex so it no longer
    treats `cluster status: not ready` as ready (substring match bug).

 -- Alex Lutay <alex.lutay@canonical.com>  Wed, 13 May 2026 11:35:00 +0000

